#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"Create simple, elegant footnotes on your site. Use the <code>[ref note="
"\"My note.\" /]</code> shortcode (<code>[ref note=\"My note.\"]My marker.[/"
"ref]</code>) and the plugin takes care of the rest. There's also a <a href="
"\"options-reading.php\">setting</a> that enables you to move the footnotes "
"below your page links, for those who paginate posts."
msgstr ""

